cu.explanation_en: Setting the tracking area code to 65536 exceeds the valid range (0-65535), causing PLMN configuration errors and network registration failures.

du.explanation_en: Setting the preamble transmission max to 100 exceeds the valid range (0-10), leading to improper RACH procedure handling and UE access failures.
du.explanation_zh: 將前導傳輸最大值設定為 100 超過有效範圍 (0-10)，導致 RACH 程序處理不當，並造成 UE 接入失敗。
